div.p:
                  A. Godfathers and Godmothers in Baptiſm;


1. Are Witneſſes of that which is done.

2. They are Sureties for performance of that which is to be done.

So that in Remiſſion or Forgiveneſs of ſins we are to conſider;


1. The Cauſes of this Forgiveneſs, without us.


2. The Conditions required thereunto, within us.

                  A. Becauſe there is taught in this Sacrament;


1. A Communion between Chriſt and us.

2. A Communion between us Chriſtians among our ſelves one with another.
